GET http://localhost:8080/me
Authorization: daf83338-e8c1-4d83-a1c5-f2846e20c575

### 03 登录管理员 tom，获取 ADMIN token
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "tom",
  "password": "123456"
}

