### 09 注册临时用户，测试 insert
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "mybatis_test",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 10 管理员删除临时用户，测试 deleteByUsername
DELETE http://localhost:8080/admin/users/mybatis_test
Authorization: 525f19d7-4bb4-4ce2-ac61-b5d38e0f0bb5

### 11 普通用户退出登录，测试 clearToken
POST http://localhost:8080/logout
Authorization: 583c0c16-2cfc-4ce0-a689-610027ed934a

### 12 退出后用旧 token 访问 /me，应该失败
GET http://localhost:8080/me
Authorization: 583c0c16-2cfc-4ce0-a689-610027ed934a